Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.13,1:12:29.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Guns are mine.\N{\rCHT}槍是我的武器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.61,1:12:47.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I help you fellas?\N{\rCHT}有什麼需要幫忙的麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.65,1:12:50.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey. - Forty - five - caliber bullets.\N{\rCHT}- 嘿 - 45口徑子彈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.99,1:12:52.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Uh...\N{\rCHT}呃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.24,1:12:54.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I only have... - We'll take them all.\N{\rCHT}- 我只有 - 我們全部帶走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.66,1:12:56.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just do what he says. He won't hurt you.\N{\rCHT}按他說的做 他不會傷害你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.70,1:12:57.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't want any trouble.\N{\rCHT}我不想惹上什麼麻煩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.62,1:13:00.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're smarter than most.\N{\rCHT}那好 你比大多數人都聰明的多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.66,1:13:01.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hurry up...\N{\rCHT}快點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.39,1:13:15.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get you somewhere safe.\N{\rCHT}走吧 帶你去個安全的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:17.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gunslinger.\N{\rCHT}槍俠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.77,1:13:22.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me?\N{\rCHT}你想我了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.31,1:13:27.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you did.\N{\rCHT}我覺得 你肯定想我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.90,1:13:29.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Roland! Roland, Roland.\N{\rCHT}羅蘭 羅蘭 羅蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.86,1:13:31.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jake, run.\N{\rCHT}傑克 快跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.69,1:13:32.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Run!\N{\rCHT}快跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.29,1:13:46.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,I see you finally found a compass, yet you still came to me.\N{\rCHT}我猜你找到了指南針的話 肯定還會來找我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.00,1:13:49.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because I'm your only destination, Roland.\N{\rCHT}因為我才是你唯一的 目標 羅蘭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.21,1:13:52.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fire away.\N{\rCHT}開火{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.55,1:13:56.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not me. I'm not doing this.\N{\rCHT}這不是我 我控制不住自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.81,1:14:01.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,First, you want to save the Tower.\N{\rCHT}首先 你想保住黑暗塔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.14,1:14:04.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then, kill the Man in Black.\N{\rCHT}然後 你想殺掉黑衣人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.23,1:14:12.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are like a dog fetching a stick over and over.\N{\rCHT}你就像狗一樣 反反復複的把扔出去的棍子叼回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.57,1:14:15.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,You tell the kid what happened to the old crew?\N{\rCHT}你有沒有告訴那個孩子老一代槍俠是怎麼死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.24,1:14:18.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You tell him that everyone that walks with you dies by my hand?\N{\rCHT}你有沒有告訴他 每個在你身邊的人都死在了我的手裡嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.91,1:14:20.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not this time.\N{\rCHT}這次不會了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.33,1:14:22.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your soft-skinned mother?\N{\rCHT}你的媽媽 皮膚軟軟的喲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.29,1:14:24.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Your Gunslinger friends? - Face me.\N{\rCHT}- 還有你的槍俠朋友們 - 跟我當面對峙啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.37,1:14:25.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your whimpering excuse for a dad.\N{\rCHT}你在你那垂死的老父親面前哭嚎著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.12,1:14:29.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop hiding behind your magic and face me, Walter!\N{\rCHT}別天天擺弄你的魔法了 沃爾特 出來跟我當面對峙啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.50,1:14:34.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,We both know that no matter who crosses the finish line first...\N{\rCHT}我們都知道我們倆無論誰先死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.63,1:14:37.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,...the universe will die out eventually.\N{\rCHT}宇宙終將消亡的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.14,1:14:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Death always wins.\N{\rCHT}死亡才是勝者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.56,1:14:42.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's the deal.\N{\rCHT}就是如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.65,1:14:52.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, no.\N{\rCHT}不 不{\r}
