Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.49,1:15:45.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are the full package, as advertised.\N{\rCHT}正如傳言的那樣 你這孩子天賦異稟啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.37,1:15:49.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sayre, get ready.\N{\rCHT}賽爾 做好準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.00,1:15:53.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Tall, dark and handsome is about to crash the party.\N{\rCHT}有個又高又黑又帥的傢伙要來搞破壞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.77,1:16:15.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go! Move, move!\N{\rCHT}我們走 快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.11,1:16:17.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Take one and go.\N{\rCHT}拿上槍就走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.66,1:16:26.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alrighty. Let's go put everyone out of their misery, shall we?\N{\rCHT}好了 我們走 讓所有人都脫離苦海 怎麼樣{\r}
