Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.15,1:17:00.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Be careful.\N{\rCHT}小心點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.82,1:17:01.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hang on.\N{\rCHT}堅持住{\r}
