Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.35,1:19:36.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Why do you resist?\N{\rCHT}你為什麼要反抗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.77,1:19:38.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your visions didn't bring you to him, they brought you to me.\N{\rCHT}你的幻象不是指引你去找他 而是來找我{\r}
