Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.86,1:19:45.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,In fact, he's been using you this entire time to get to me.\N{\rCHT}實際上 他這段時間一直利用你來找我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.36,1:19:48.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is why you're here. This is your destiny.\N{\rCHT}這就是你為什麼在這兒 這是你的宿命{\r}
