Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.77,1:21:02.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N{\rCHT}等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.27,1:21:06.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. It's the kid.\N{\rCHT}我的天 是那個孩子幹的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.86,1:21:09.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the kid! He's keeping the portal open!\N{\rCHT}他讓那個入口保持開啟狀態{\r}
